		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Very Rare</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>These horseshoes come in a set of four. As a Action, you can touch one of the horseshoes to the hoof of a horse or similar creature, whereupon the horseshoe affixes itself to the hoof. Removing a horseshoe also takes a Action.</p></li><li><p>While all four shoes are affixed to the hooves of a horse or similar creature, they allow the creature to move normally while floating 4 inches above a surface. This effect means the creature can cross or stand above nonsolid or unstable surfaces, such as water or lava. The creature leaves no tracks and ignores &amp;Reference[Difficult Terrain]. In addition, the creature can travel for up to 12 hours a day without gaining &amp;Reference[Exhaustion] levels from extended travel.</p></li></ul>",
